Class Item

java.lang.Object
pt.ipp.isep.dei.esoft.project.domain.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Item>
public class Item extends Object implements Comparable<Item>
Represents an item that has a unique ID, a priority level, and a list of operations it needs to undergo.
